类 RecipeIngredient

java.lang.Object
dao.mappers.RecipeIngredient
public class RecipeIngredient extends Object
RecipeIngredient represents an ingredient used in a recipe with its nutritional information. This class stores ingredient details including quantity, unit, and nutritional values such as calories, protein, fat, and carbohydrates per unit.
从以下版本开始:
1.0

      public RecipeIngredient(int recipeId, String name, Float quantity, String unit, String description, Float unitCalories, Float unitProtein, Float unitFat, Float unitCarbohydrates)
      Constructor for RecipeIngredient with complete nutritional information.
      参数:
      recipeId - The ID of the recipe this ingredient belongs to
      name - The name of the ingredient
      quantity - The quantity of the ingredient
      unit - The unit of measurement
      description - Additional description of the ingredient
      unitCalories - Calories per unit of the ingredient

      unitCarbohydrates - Carbohydrate content per unit
